 1999-21231999-11-300,  ,  ,  ,  HEALTH
PrecisRe-appointment, effective January 18, 2000, of DR. HENRY FRIESEN, of Nepean, Ontario, as President of the Medical Research Council to hold office during pleasure for a term of six months, or until such time as the legislation establishing the Canadian Institutes of Health Research comes into force and the Medical Research Council is disolved, should this occur prior to the expiry of his term.
